dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. At upper right: "No. VII." Below neat line: "zu Ebelings Erdbeschreibung von Amerika." Intended for publication as part of Sotzmann, Amerikanischer atlas, Hamburg, 1796-1810. Shows county and some township boundaries. Engraved map. References: Proc. Amer. Antiq. Soc., Oct. 1925, p. 289.
